         <abstract>
            <p>This paper gives a theory of spectral approximation for closed operators in Banach spaces. The perturbation theory developed in this paper is applied to the study of a finite element procedure for approximating the spectral properties of a differential system modeling a fluid in a rotating basin.</p>
          </abstract>
